{"tid":241093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：我會體諒警署人員的疏忽，被神偷盜竊電腦線藏起吊頸","createTime":"2017-05-13T01:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T12:09:17.000Z","uid":30807,"like":10,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82eb90a9d891dde538015f3797c2079d0f89320f","tid":241093,"uid":30807,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"陳雲：強姦犯吊頸，再思考傅科（Michel Foucault）。九龍灣天橋底姦劫案的疑犯吊頸身亡，好多人都在談論羈留室如何搜身、如何無樑，如何用人手及電視監察，以防止疑犯自殺。大家並無心要賦予這些現代監察的合法性，但討論的時候已經肯定了這些現代監察和扣留程序的合法性。<br />\n<br />\n傅科羨慕的，不是這些，他也許和我一樣，在追思王朝時期。即使是最嚴密的滿清王朝在京城的天牢，俠客大刀王五都可以強闖入去，試圖救出文人譚嗣同。這些滿清獄卒懶懶散散，賭博、飲酒、打瞌睡、收賄賂，剋扣犯人的飯菜錢，王朝的監牢毫無合法性，囚犯有命出獄之後，被鄉民視為度過監牢難關的英雄好漢。<br />\n<br />\n（後記：故此，而且我會因此而認為那些偶然懶散的香港警察仍然是有人性的。）<br />\n<br />\nIQ閱讀門檻：145，歷來最高。"},{"pid":"a313622e4d52f4ed3fe935fc096bd23ceb64e597","tid":241093,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5da954c938b1540958baf73961df270e6ad384d","tid":241093,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:05:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蒼崎青子你隻五毛狗又斷章取義！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1699df8716f80134bbfbbee4b04f8816920f2cdc","tid":241093,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蒼崎青子你隻五毛狗又斷章取義！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/