e=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蒼崎青子你隻五毛狗又斷章取義！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛狗出沒注意！9527~ #48157</span><br />\n五毛同雜種有親「習大大」+ 打殘體字</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tg8us6vx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftg8us6vx&h=2fc572aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160423/845373/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20160423%2F845373%2F&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d53af4ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160423/845373/</a><br />\n中共官媒過去為中國國家主席習近平打造親民形象工程，經常在報道或微博上稱呼他為「習大大」，其夫人彭麗媛則被稱為「彭麻麻」。<br />\n<ins><strong><em>大陸傳媒仲用「習大大」！</em></strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/y/2017-04-26/doc-ifyetwsm0490871.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fstock%2Fy%2F2017-04-26%2Fdoc-ifyetwsm0490871.shtml&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=537d9683\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/y/2017-04-26/doc-ifyetwsm0490871.shtml</a><br />\n2017-04-26<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cppcc.china.com.cn/2017-04/12/content_40604898.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcppcc.china.com.cn%2F2017-04%2F12%2Fcontent_40604898.htm&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6f7de159\" target=\"_blank\">http://cppcc.china.com.cn/2017-04/12/content_40604898.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bn8uelhs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbn8uelhs&h=34597b6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017-04-12"},{"pid":"42b5246facba3bde3514c2139319d73102e00df9","tid":241093,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"即係政府及警察執行公務並沒有其正當合法性 大家係可以劫獄"},{"pid":"0356fbf3c97d4490398f00bc00c3b35b459eab6a","tid":241093,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b4de5a9200c3fb78a6b820268f2448e230c23ce","tid":241093,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳雲：強姦犯吊頸，再思考傅科（Michel Foucault）。九龍灣天橋底姦劫案的疑犯吊頸身亡，好多人都在談論羈留室如何搜身、如何無樑，如何用人手及電視監察，以防止疑犯自殺。大家並無心要賦予這些現代監察的合法性，但討論的時候已經肯定了這些現代監察和扣留程序的合法性。<br />\n<br />\n傅科羨慕的，不是這些，他也許和我一樣，在追思王朝時期。即使是最嚴密的滿清王朝在京城的天牢，俠客大刀王五都可以強闖入去，試圖救出文人譚嗣同。這些滿清獄卒懶懶散散，賭博、飲酒、打瞌睡、收賄賂，剋扣犯人的飯菜錢，王朝的監牢毫無合法性，囚犯有命出獄之後，被鄉民視為度過監牢難關的英雄好漢。<br />\n<br />\n（後記：故此，而且我會因此而認為那些偶然懶散的香港警察仍然是有人性的。）<br />\n<br />\nIQ閱讀門檻：145，歷來最高。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你閱讀理解真係好撚有問題，返去小學啦。<br />\n</span></span>竟然可以解讀成「陳雲：我會體諒警署人員的疏忽，被神偷盜竊電腦線藏起吊頸」"},{"pid":"8fb54037b11e4db43aa8c187fae18f772eb1077e","tid":241093,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />on9"},{"pid":"a2ca337fccb19e22f186c44241faee72ce0cc94c","tid":241093,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面都好似好直，但最尾又加多句<br />\n<br />\n這些滿清獄卒懶懶散散，賭博、飲酒、打瞌睡、收賄賂，剋扣犯人的飯菜錢，王朝的監牢毫無合法性<br />\n<br />\n嘩，我真係睇唔明佢up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果呢個文章抽走幾句野，的確可以視為曲線 但係&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"