版陶傑為警察護航打呢個文章，係極高明。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「如果由一個藍絲版陶傑為警察護航打呢個文章，係極高明。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有嚟FF，「警察護航打呢個文章」</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你用拚音打字？點會又黎會變左有黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我唔會好似你屈9527係五毛咁屈返你放心，屈話五毛除非係有壓倒性證據，否則根本只係削弱緊自己講野既權威性，不過陳雲FAN可能慣左圍爐冇所謂啦。<br />\n<br />\n我身邊都有土生土長既香港人打拚音既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  OK<br />\n<br />\n覆返你正題，你到底講乜鬼野，我指如果，係如果<br />\n<br />\n冇話陳雲係呢個立場，FF左D乜野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25917d673d35b7af0b320c9abf1eac58bd486ef","tid":241093,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死返政事台啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSORRY <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c3b945c842a5010cb9190eaa0ba40c728da993","tid":241093,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"其實我係#69 講果樣野好簡單易明姐<br />\n你有正常智商都一定明我講咩<br />\n何必特登扮唔明，顧左右而言他呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果你係真心唔明，咁我道歉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c2e47d9d4cb245c23a0f375429837601f89b6f","tid":241093,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我睇得明<br />\n係咪我有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明呢，就唔係明唔到<br />\n<br />\n不過要符合返陳雲自命既立場，就會有矛盾<br />\n<br />\n如果由一個藍絲版陶傑為警察護航打呢個文章，係極高明。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「如果由一個藍絲版陶傑為警察護航打呢個文章，係極高明。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有嚟FF，「警察護航打呢個文章」</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你用拚音打字？點會又黎會變左有黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />